4.77/5  rDev +7.9%look: 4 | smell: 4.5 | taste: 5 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 5Poured from 22oz bottle. Many thanks go out to Luke (Lukafer) who cracked this one open at the last tasting. Good luck in Indy Luke!
